snippet.title: RAWMEN Devs Explain Meatballs & Boba Balls
snippet.description:
Visit https://rawmengame.com/ to subscribe to newsletter!
And join official Discord server at https://discord.gg/RAWMEN to chat with community and the devs and participate in our future playtests.

RAWMEN is a radical multiplayer arena shooter that pits you against 2-8 of your closest taste buds or foes. Channel your inner souperiority and unleash culinary devastation for good. 

Here’s a sample of what’s on the menu:
- Claim Chowder: Defend the coveted chowder pot from the enemy players to win!
- Meatball: Jump into the comforting warmth of the juicy meat and roll your way to the goal; just don't get knocked out, WE NEED THAT MEAT JUICE!
- Top RAWMEN: Use your doughnut bombs to launch yourself in the air and traverse obstacles, all the while collecting the most prized possession: Golden Bouillon Cubes!
...and much more!

More info at https://rawmengame.com/
